@startuml MyAIStorybook_Sequence_Character_Chat
title MyAIStorybook - Sequence Diagram: Character Chat Interaction

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend\n(Next.js)" as Frontend
participant "FastAPI\nBackend" as Backend
participant "ChatbotAgent" as Chatbot
participant "Ollama\nLLM" as LLM
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Frontend: Select character to chat with
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/chat\n{story_id, character_name, user_message}
activate Backend

Backend -> DB: Get story data
activate DB
DB --> Backend: Story with characters
deactivate DB

Backend -> Chatbot: chat(story_context, character, message)
activate Chatbot

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Build character prompt\nwith story context

Chatbot -> LLM: Generate character response\n(2-4 sentences, child-friendly)
activate LLM
LLM --> Chatbot: Character response
deactivate LLM

Chatbot --> Backend: Response text
deactivate Chatbot

Backend -> DB: Save conversation\n(conversation_id, messages)
activate DB
DB --> Backend: Saved
deactivate DB

Backend --> Frontend: {response, character}
deactivate Backend

Frontend -> Frontend: Display character response\nin chat interface
Frontend --> User: Show character message
deactivate Frontend

@enduml
